{"tid":1631883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣 Brainstorm","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:18.000Z","uid":80143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"95bea976dfbd14f42ee926e70abc34ef264fc014","tid":1631883,"uid":80143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:13.000Z","msg":"之前有非面式統計，文宣組人數係最少的<br />\n<br />\n普遍人成日話勇武同和理非出去做野，等文宣包底，但你地有無諗過做一份文宣要用幾多時間同精神？<br />\n<br />\n每日出去發完夢，文宣守尾門唔訓，整合每日唔同精華然後做production，諗起都知難做。<br />\n<br />\n另外，自從星期五緊急法後，民怨四起，勇武步伐太快，令到國際聲音或報導開始轉風向，而家真係需要大量文宣幫大家帶返風句，但唔好得個講字。<br />\n<br />\n無論你識唔識用photoshop或者剪片，最基本要做幾樣野：<br />\n1. 裝fb, ig, twitter, reddit 每日幫手禁幾個掣宣傳；<br />\n2. 落街印、派、貼<br />\n3. 最重要最重要最重要，文宣組其實多數都係和理非，佢地都會出去發夢，返到屋企好攰仲要度橋做文宣真係好晒精力，所以我地要幫手：每人每日靜十幾分鐘，brainstorm一個idea (或者手畫) 出黎俾靈感手足做野！"},{"pid":"e461ae0fb546a6c4e5fcc1ef2ad3252c5ccada67","tid":1631883,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:12.000Z","msg":"邊個大大聲話集中<br />\n<br />\n鞭屍時間<br />\n<br />\n集中撚答到我問題，先好叫人出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"49f144aff96457bcc487807423673dea8e318959","tid":1631883,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"f64dc96e5ea436217774b36992908a442e20878a","tid":1631883,"uid":167340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和理非做盾幫勇武頂嘅時候到了<br />\n<br />\n文宣~! </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4ab00d8a3e1f2dbaa1d97b205cacf3b23ff6626a","tid":1631883,"uid":265339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:42.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布！聽日係全民文宣日！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631729\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631729</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e7cbeddcf9e22e1cbad0f21df3e63475874d13fd","tid":1631883,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣開工</span></span>"},{"pid":"2b5dc3aa0b8536e550383d9bffe2c1abb672a45c","tid":1631883,"uid":80143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"我先！<br />\n<br />\n林鄭專登揀星期五宣佈引用緊急法推禁蒙面法，配合埋星期六電視講話要人同勇武割席，仲有星期日聲明，再配合商場地鐵罷市，派大量卧底故亂破壞，製造民不擾生景象，製造更多對立，令人民對人民，司馬昭之心已經路人皆見<br />\n<br />\n建議用一個沙盤推算既表，向外宣掦林鄭想要既目的，列晒出黎，之後是但中一樣都可以證明到條柒婆唔撚係有心幫香港，例如阻止美國通過民主法案、口說對法內裡捕盡年青一代...etc"},{"pid":"fb02e1c45e59bfcf080d87d980cac2b56f0fb45f","tid":1631883,"uid":133649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3bc6931033a87340ed01d6155bd2c0e0b9e3771a","tid":1631883,"uid":80143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">諗呀！！！</span></span><br />\n咪撚再理d互屌分化post, 咩港唔港島私唔私了<br />\n唔好再打咀炮要人老奉幫你做文宣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">諗呀！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f42f45e34bbacf2abc19d7e505f3a4a49731267e","tid":1631883,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"其實如果想幫手整文宣可以點加入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f538aa8c2e08f6e4316bb3c18f7406fb646fc6e","tid":1631883,"uid":80143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:46:18.000Z","msg":"上緊連登既你 一個二個放低電話 暫時遠離連登！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631560</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個post講得好岩，要靠自己理性去調節，靜一靜，幫文宣諗下idea<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>思想呀求下大家</strong></span></span>"}]}